

= Strategist (Sales & Trading) - Career Pathways

This document outlines career progression for strategist roles in Sales & Trading divisions at investment banks and financial institutions, with a focus on the Australian market. Strategists combine macroeconomic analysis with market insights to provide clients with actionable investment recommendations across asset classes.

