Create supporting appendix with detailed data, model methodology, historical analysis. Send to senior strategist for review before tomorrow's presentations.

*4:00pm - 5:00pm*: Weekly strategy team meeting with Head of Strategy and all strategists (rates, FX, commodities, equities, credit). Each strategist presents key calls and debates upcoming research priorities.

You present AUD/bond call update: "Maintaining bearish AUD (target 0.6400) and bullish Aus bonds (target 3.25%). Fed hawkish minutes overnight validated our divergence thesis. Recommend keeping these as flagship calls for Q4."

